        <Summary>Service-menus for image processing</Summary>
        <Description>"KDE Image Menu", shortly Kim, is an image service menu for the file manager Dolphin and Konqueror with many usefull features like compressing, resizing, converting, rotating, resizing and send by mail, rename and more other actions.</Description>
        <Archive type="targz" sha1sum="1bbc85543c46c04420adb0491683c79d2ff1d142">http://bouveyron.free.fr/kim/release/kim4-0.9.5.tar.gz</Archive>
